<h2 id="a-navigation-y-slide">A navigation-y slide</h2>
<p>As <a href="http://russelldavies.typepad.com/planning/2015/06/doing-the-hard-work-to-make-it-bearable.html">Russell says,</a> your talk should have some kind of structure and you should tell people what that structure is. I like to use a different colour background my navigation and structure slides.</p>

