<h2 id="a-slide-for-quotes">A slide for quotes</h2>
<p>Quoting people in talks is good. Have a design for that. Make sure thereâ€™s somewhere visible for the attribution of the quote. Attributions are both classy <em>and</em> mean people can look stuff up later.</p>

