<h2 id="a-slide-for-showing-a-picture-of-a-website">A slide for showing a picture of a website</h2>
<p>YMMV but I show a lot of pictures of websites in my talks. Make sure theyâ€™re are as big as possible, nobody needs to see all that browser chrome. Make sure thereâ€™s a place for the url of the page (leaving the address bar in will be too small).</p>

