<h2 id="a-slide-for-your-power-quotes">A slide for your â€œpower quotesâ€</h2>

<p>Before I spoke at Nordic.js, they asked me for my talkâ€™s â€œpower quotesâ€ so that as I gave my talk, they could tweet the important bits. This is quite a good idea really, it helps get the thing you want to say in front of more people. To help my points carry further, I put the really important stuff on itâ€™s own slide and make sure itâ€™s big enough to photograph from the audience.</p>

